#: 09.2-Live-Loops.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"live_loop :foo do\n"
"  play 60\n"
"  sleep 1\n"
"end"
msgstr ""
"live_loop :foo do\n"
"  play 60\n"
"  sleep 1\n"
"end"

#: 09.2-Live-Loops.md:22
msgid ""
"Now press the Run button. You hear a basic beep every beat. Nothing fun there."
" However, don't press Stop just yet. Change the `60` to `65` and press Run aga"
